Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<User>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Attendee, Organizer, Speaker
    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<User>, java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the properties and actions of all users. They all have a name, address, email, username, and password.
